  "summary": "## Summary: Panduan Pengguna Frontend UI Aplikasi Arumanis\n\n### Changes Implemented\n- Explored full codebase structure: `src/features/` (auth, dashboard, kegiatan, desa, kecamatan, pekerjaan, output, kontrak, penerima, penyedia, berkas, foto, users, roles, permissions, route-permissions, settings, audit-logs, etc.), `src/components/ui/` (40 components), `src/components/layout/` (15 components), `src/config/ability.ts`, `src/features/auth/` (login flow with email/password + Google OAuth).\n- Created `docs/user-guide/` and `docs/assets/screenshots/` directories.\n- Wrote 18 Markdown documentation files in `docs/user-guide/`, each covering: URL path, tujuan fitur, field data & validasi, langkah penggunaan, aksi tabel, notifikasi/error, perilaku khusus role.\n- Index file links all modules and cross-references supplementary guides.\n\n### Files Modified\n- `docs/user-guide/index.md` — main navigation & table of contents\n- `docs/user-guide/navigasi-global.md` — layout, sidebar menu (all groups & items), header, breadcrumb, fiscal year, search, theme toggle, impersonation banner\n- `docs/user-guide/auth.md` — login (email/password + Google), form validation, session, logout, role-specific redirect (pengawas SSO handoff)\n- `docs/user-guide/dashboard.md` — KegiatanStats (9 metrics), 10 chart types, DataQualityStats, Analytics trend/regional/category, fiscal year & kecamatan filters\n- `docs/user-guide/kegiatan.md` — 7 fields including kode, sumber dana, pagu; CRUD, relational delete protection\n- `docs/user-guide/desa-kecamatan.md` — kecamatan (5 fields) + desa (5 fields), GeoJSON for mapping\n- `docs/user-guide/pekerjaan-output.md` — pekerjaan (12 fields), draft pekerjaan, output (7 fields), register dokumen\n- `docs/user-guide/kontrak.md` — kontrak (8 fields, 4 statuses), addendum (6 fields)\n- `docs/user-guide/penerima-penyedia.md` — penerima (10 fields incl. NIK, KK, komunal/individu), penyedia (8 fields incl. NPWP)\n- `docs/user-guide/berkas-foto.md` — berkas upload (5 fields, 7 document types), foto upload (6 fields, grid gallery), MediaCard, file size/format limits\n- `docs/user-guide/users.md` — user CRUD (8 fields), role assignment, password management, admin-only access\n- `docs/user-guide/roles-permissions.md` — roles, permissions, route permissions (path+method+allowed roles), kegiatan role, menu permissions; admin bypass logic\n- `docs/user-guide/settings.md` — app settings, audit trail, debug reporting, assign pekerjaan, broadcast notifikasi, WhatsApp integration\n- `docs/user-guide/komponen-ui-dasar.md` — 30+ UI components: button, card, table, select/async-search, modal, sheet, badge, skeleton, chart, toast, tabs, command menu (Ctrl+K), etc.\n- `docs/user-guide/skenario-penggunaan.md` — 6 cross-module scenarios (input kegiatan→dokumentasi, kontrak→addendum, cari penerima, review progress, user+role management, data troubleshooting)\n- `docs/user-guide/manajemen-akses.md` — RBAC levels (admin/operator/viewer/pengawas), route permission decision flowchart, impersonation\n- `docs/user-guide/pemecahan-masalah.md` — error tables for login, 403, 404, upload, form validation, data relations, network, session, browser issues; step-by-step recovery guide\n- `docs/user-guide/glosarium.md` — 30+ domain terms (ARUMANIS, Pagu, RAB, RBAC, SPAM, Route Permission, Kegiatan Role, dll)\n\n### Notes for Developer\n- All docs are in Indonesian for end users (operator desa/kecamatan, admin).\n- Placeholder screenshot paths reference `docs/assets/screenshots/` — need actual UI screenshots captured and saved there.\n- `index.md` links to all files for searchable navigation.\n- The sign-in page link at `src/features/auth/sign-in/index.tsx:46` points to `/docs/index.html` — consider routing to `/docs/user-guide/index.html` or adjusting the href.\n- Ready for UI/UX team review before publication.",
  "justFinishedAt": "2026-06-19T04:07:26.598Z"
}